  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate feasibility and efficacy of rituximab-bendamustine
      (R-B)combination in elderly patients affected by diffuse large B-cell lymphoma and defined as
      frail according to CGA.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
